720037f-a.title: Manhattan: Gramercy Park East - Gramercy Park (South)
720037f-a.text:
34, and 36 Gramercy Park East, at and adjoining the N.E. corner of Gramercy Park South, showing the Gramercy Park (9-stories) and the Gramercy Park Club Apartments (12-stories), as seen from Irving Place (extreme foreground), Gramercy Park South and across Gramercy Park.
July 7, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
